TextEng: "You have a funny way of speaking."
"Why are you so concerned that I might have been followed?"
Text: "왜 내가 뒤쫓겨 왔을까 봐 그렇게 걱정해?"

TextEng: "What makes you think I've escaped from somewhere?"
"But I'm really not a slave. I never have been."
Text: "하지만 난 정말 노예가 아니야. 한 번도 아니었어."

TextEng: "Why don't you rise up and overthrow them?"
"What are you going to do now?"
"What, you think I did it for you?"
Text: "뭐, 내가 너를 위해 한 것 같아?"

TextEng: "You're welcome. I'm grateful for the chance to help."
